    Compilation: javac Rational.java Execution: java Rational Immutable ADT for Rational numbers. Invariants ----------- - gcd(num, den) = 1, i.e, the rational number is in reduced form - den >= 1, the denominator is always a positive integer - 0/1 is the unique representation of 0 We employ some tricks to stave off overflow, but if you need arbitrary precision rationals, use BigRational.java. % java Rational 5/6 1 1/120000000 1073741789/12 1 841/961 -1/3
